BrainSpace-class         package:NeuroImage         R Documentation

_C_l_a_s_s "_B_r_a_i_n_S_p_a_c_e"

_D_e_s_c_r_i_p_t_i_o_n:

     BrainSpace represents the topology of a dataset

_O_b_j_e_c_t_s _f_r_o_m _t_h_e _C_l_a_s_s:

     Objects can be created by calls of the form 'BrainSpace(Dim,
     dimension, spacing, origin) '.

_S_l_o_t_s:


     '_D_i_m': Object of class '"integer"' - an integer array specifiying
          the spatial dimensions 

     '_o_r_i_g_i_n': Object of class '"numeric"' - an array representing the
          absolute location of the origin (coordinate at voxel [0, 0,
          0]) 

     '_s_p_a_c_i_n_g': Object of class '"numeric"' - an array representing the
          grid spacing for each dimension       

     '_o_r_i_e_n_t_a_t_i_o_n': Object of class '"character"' - character array
          describing axes orientation, e.g., "L" for "left-right", "P"
          for "posterior-anterior", "I" for "inferior-superior". This
          slot is currently not used and may contain invalid
          information.

     '_t_r_a_n_s': Object of class '"matrix"' - This is a transformation
          matrix used for computing the mapping from index coordinates
          to real world oordiantes. Should be a 4X4 matrix for
          volumetrix data.

     '_i_n_v_T_r_a_n_s': Object of class '"matrix"' - This is the inverse
          transformation (real world to index) and is computed
          internally and therefore should not be changed externally 

     '_r_e_p_t_i_m_e': Object of class '"numeric"' - The delay between volume
          acquisitions in seconds 


_M_e_t_h_o_d_s:


     _b_o_u_n_d_s 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the real world
          bounds as a matrix of (min, max) pairs 

     _i_n_v_T_r_a_n_s 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the dimension of
          the data axes for the space 

     _n_u_m_d_i_m 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the number of
          dimensions in space 

     _o_r_i_e_n_t_a_t_i_o_n 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the
          (currently unsupported) orientation code  

     _o_r_i_g_i_n 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the coordinate
          origin 

     _s_p_a_c_i_n_g 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the voxel spacing 

     _t_r_a_n_s<- 'signature(x = "BrainSpace", value = "matrix")': - returns
          the index-to-word transformation matrix 

     _t_r_a_n_s 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the inverse
          transformation matrix 

     _r_e_p_t_i_m_e 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - returns the repetition
          time 

     _s_h_o_w 'signature(x = "BrainSpace")': - print information about
          BrainSpace object 


_A_u_t_h_o_r(_s):

     Bradley Buchsbaum bbuchsbaum@berkeley.edu

_R_e_f_e_r_e_n_c_e_s:

